niversities in Nigeria. It did seem that his academic ambition would be realized as his academic career flourished. However, this was not to be as a greater career awaited him in the service of the Lord. In 1967 Enoch Adeboye got married to his beloved wife <strong>Foluke Adenike Adeboye (nee Adeyokunnu).</strong></p><h3>OUR VISION AND MISSION</h3><p>As received by the General Overseer (G.O.), Pastor E. A. Adeboye, and communicated to the Headquarters leaders, our vision and mission statement shall remain intact, with a qualifying addendum in view of the peculiarity of the demography in the North American region. They are as follows:<br />1. To make heaven.<br />2. To take as many people with us.<br />3. To have a member of RCCG in every family of all nations.<br />4. To accomplish No. 1 above, holiness will be our lifestyle.<br />5. To accomplish No. 2 and 3 above, we will plant churches within five minutes walking distance in every city and town of developing countries and within five minutes driving distance in every city and town of developed countries.<br /><br />We will pursue these objectives until every Nation in the world is reached for the Lord Jesus Christ</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:5:{s:5:\"class\";s:30:\"WP_Widget_Black_Studio_TinyMCE\";s:4:\"grid\";i:0;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:0;s:5:\"style\";a:2:{s:27:\"background_image_attachment\";b:0;s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:1;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:28:\"https://youtu.be/vFunbHN7noo\";s:11:\"panels_info\";a:6:{s:5:\"class\";s:19:\"Sydney_Video_Widget\";s:3:\"raw\";b:0;s:4:\"grid\";i:1;s:4:\"cell\";i:0;s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:5:\"style\";a:1:{s:18:\"background_display\";s:4:\"tile\";}}}i:2;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"action_text\";s:56:\"TO BE PART OF THIS GREAT FAMILY FEEL FREE TO CONTACT US \";s:15:\"action_btn_link\";s:45:\"http://localhost/church/index.php/contact-us/\";s:15:\"action_btn_text\";s:10:\"Contact US\";s:6:\"inline\";b:0;s:11:\"p